     H            Y.
     F** CHKR19 *******************************************************
     F* GET QUICK IPL FLAG                                            *
     F* CREATE DATE : 2018.08.06                                      *
     F* AUTHOR      : J.WATANABE                                      *
     F* FUNCTION    : SET FALG Y OR N                                 *
     F*               WHEN FLAG=Y, IPL SKIPS FILE REORGANIZE PROCESS  *
     F*****************************************************************
     FAB#PPCK IF  E           K        DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------
      * PARAMETER
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $FLAG   1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $FLAG
      *--------------------------------------------------
      *  MAIN ROUTINE
      *--------------------------------------------------
     C                     MOVEL'QIPL'    $KEY1  10 P
     C           $KEY1     CHAINAB#PPCK              90
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVELCKSFLG    $FLAG
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
